Joseph Oliver Launchbury (born 12 April 1991) is an English rugby union lock who plays for Premiership side Wasps.  
He represents England at international level and previously played for the under-18s and under-20s before making his Test debut in 2012.
Launchbury plays mainly in the second row but is also comfortable as a blindside flanker. His nickname in the England set up is "Launchers".
